{"id": "2d8b06fa7732c373f7e55b9fca009d60fb4dd4111df6ad0ba58da2855f35cde3", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:0", "text": "You can add a RenderMan IPR ROP from the"}
{"id": "bcd220fd0366683bd6a92943b39cd21fbf0477f918c1ba7fe724f1316c2cf1a9", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:5", "text": "RenderMan Shelf"}
{"id": "39bbf500a316d6e9f6cc3a9e3d262088c077cb40e0255e91b4a92fb2490c9ece", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:2", "text": "or from the /out pane."}
{"id": "c7da25857d287595bf3d553838fc56e313bd22acae9bd98a5306223dcda1e9aa", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:3", "text": "Using RenderMan Shelf"}
{"id": "035d810150068e0cce1b2f7cbad8b3b30c17e4f25bb643ee1d6f5ee97cf206fe", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:4", "text": "We can use the ROP tool in the"}
{"id": "e42f47e1af122366bccf238fff42184f9ae13b0b8fb44afc3bcd0b5ce9dd91f2", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:6", "text": "to create a ROP that automatically adds an integrator VOP to your RIS Network."}
{"id": "0ff2aae666a6fec465d1d142cdbb0a7b4527111aa78cc18ee10c382472380ca6", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:7", "text": "Using out pane (Manual Configuration)"}
{"id": "4090cbb7afacec2fc5197874113eab7a43b75dc4d4c9b905cafc8a2202da019b", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:8", "text": "Add RenderMAN IPR ROP"}
{"id": "1062693896582cd8ba2526c5b1d2951822ff9186e67459660d48f85a98a563da", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:9", "text": "Add Integrator"}
{"id": "a09b9fc0e25a43ccbea265f55794b64c0e4e8c5d5eefbca1133c1efea6ba22c7", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:10", "text": "In your RIS Network, add an integrator VOP inside your RIS Network, e.g."}
{"id": "c66c3367fc146e7ab68fcb67ccdd75c3909cd0bca2343b35b4f46f0cbc0a6a52", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:11", "text": "PxrPathTracer"}
{"id": "bebccb340f3196f7687c289303f4d2c531967972aebb252fa232f96111a88fb1", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:12", "text": "Set the Integrator"}
{"id": "775f5de953bcdb7576d990969982f8530ad1738dfe9d7ea66b0c379ab7e0e076", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:13", "text": "Simply drag the path of your integrator VOP path to the"}
{"id": "e43f447b65e6b1236fa237ffc613d5e0dde3509a5d3089e6378686e41318d17a", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:14", "text": "Integrator"}
{"id": "b36ef3235e1311f00561825c1504a68042e9d20ff872a7d686413a61b9faf698", "item_id": "64218d3dd7:15", "text": "in RenderMan RIS ROP.  If you skip this step, by default, it will use the PxrPathTracer integrator with its default parameters."}
